      "text": "Laser Socks is a game about jumping around and shooting a laser pointer at an opponent's feet. It was fun, ridiculous, and simple to make. In some ways, Laser Socks became one of the highlight demonstrations of what could be done if there was a medium of expression that integrated dynamic computational elements into the physical world. [http://glench.com/LaserSocks/ post]"
